<p><a href="#sdfootnote9anc" name="sdfootnote9sym">9</a> Zach Sokol, <em>Bunny Rogers on her deeply intimate solo show at the Whitney</em>, „i-D Vice” z 1 września 2017, <a href="https://i-d.vice.com/en_us/article/9kkjb3/artist-bunny-rogers-wants-you-to-know-she-acknowledges-your-hurt" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://i-d.vice.com/en_us/article/9kkjb3/artist-bunny-rogers-wants-you-to-know-she-acknowledges-your-hurt</a>, dostęp 28 lutego 2018.</p>
